            <!-- WHAT IS OFF THE CUF -->
            <div class="section-card">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>What is Off the CUF?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">
                    <div class="card-content-with-image">
                        <div>
                            <p>Off the CUF is a relaxed and friendly morning gathering that takes place on the
                            first Saturday of every month. It is open to absolutely everyone — whether you are
                            part of our congregation, curious about church, or simply looking for some company
                            and a good brunch.</p>

                            <p>On the first Saturday of each month we gather in an informal café-style setting
                            to explore a theme that speaks to our shared human experience. We introduce different
                            perspectives, including Christian viewpoints, creating space for open conversation
                            where we can listen, share, and learn from each other.</p>

                            <p>Topics explored in the past include: Joy, Global aid, Peace, Olympic inspirations,
                            God's love.</p>

                            <p>There is no programme to follow and no pressure. Come along, grab a drink, have
                            some food, and see where the morning takes you. The three ingredients are simple:</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <img src="/assets/images/OfftheCUFPoster.jpg" alt="Off the CUF poster" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

